lead_paragraph: Yoenis Cespedes had an RBI infield single and reached base three times to help the New York Mets beat the Atlanta Braves 7-5 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Cespedes Gets 1st Hit of Spring, Mets Beat Braves 7-5
